data.remarks: 1. Conversion of 3,95,000 Global depository receipts into 39,50,000 Equity Shares of Vaibhav Global Limited2. This filing is being made in respect of conversion of 3,95,000 GDRs held by Sonymike's HoldingsLimited into 39,50,000 Equity Shares of Rs. 10 each. The percentage has been calculated on voting share capital of the Company which does not include 3,950000 Equity Shares issued to the custodian on account of the non voting global Depository Receipts.3. The Percentage of shares / voting rights acquired, subsequent to acquisition is based on the expanded shares capital of the Company taking into account 39,50,000 Equity Shares of Rs. 10 each transferred to Sonymike's Holdings Limited upon conversion of GDRs.
